<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <style type="text/css" media="screen">
    body { padding: 10px; background-color: #f8f8f8; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Sans-Serif; font-size: 0.8em; }
    #content { margin: 0; width: 700px; border: 1px solid #1B4E77; background-color: #fff; color: #666; padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; }
    h2 { color: #1B4E77; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1.2em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="content">
    <h2>Task Group Modification</h2>
    <p>This email is from the Equality Risk Toolkit assessment tool.</p>
    <p>You have received this email as you have been added to a Task Group aiding in the completion of the equality analysis for this policy/function.</p>
    <p>The link below will take you to the <%= @activity.name -%> summary page where you will be able to view the assessment.</p>
    <p><%= auto_link(activity_url(@activity)).html_safe %></p>
    <p>If you have any queries about the assessment process please contact a member of your Directorate Lead Equality Officer.</p>
    <p>Thank you.</p>    
  </div>
</body>
</html>